.modal.admindevmodal.fade#vjtv_modal(tabindex='-1', role='dialog', aria-labelledby='myLargeModalLabel', aria-hidden='true')
  .modal-dialog.modal-lg.modal-dialog-centered
    .modal-content.text-body
      .modal-header
        h5#myLargeModalLabel.modal-title="VJ Television the first Audio Visuals Arts channel"
        button.close(type='button', data-dismiss='modal', aria-label='Close')
          span(aria-hidden='true') ×
      .modal-body(style="line-height: 1.5;")
        p
          | VJ Television 24-hour programming born from a daily selection of contents from the biggest Audio Visuals Arts platform: 
          a(href='https://avnode.net', target='_blank', rel='noopener noreferrer')
            b AVnode.net
          |. Interested to UPLOAD contents? 
          a(href='https://vjtelevision.com/contents-programming/')
            b CLICK HERE
        p The daily programming is:
        ul
          li
            b 06:00 – 12:00 Documentary
            br
            | Here is a collection of workshops, interview and report live video related.
          li
            b 12:00 – 18:00 Video
            br
            | All those videos are made from vjs and audio visual artists so you could find a lots of differences in technical and style.
          li
            b 18:00 – 00:00 Performances
            br
            | This is the time of the audio visual performances, live cinema, mapping, generative and many other styles of live performances.
          li
            b 00:00 – 06:00 VJ-DJ Sets
            br
            | Let’s get party with the best VJ from all over the world.
        u Get VJ Television contents on demand jumping on a day from the calendar up right.
      .modal-footer
        button.btn(type='button', data-dismiss='modal')=global.__("Cancel")
        button.btn.btn-primary.disabled#loadingplay(type='button', data-dismiss='modal')
          i.icon-spinner.animate-spin.mr-2
          span!=global.__("Loading current day programming")
